Prepares external reports and presentations for clients and internal company reports for management regarding full status of a project or projects, including any potential or actual risks or project changes. May have specialized knowledge or expertise in technical or business matters that uniquely qualifies them to oversee the underlying project and team.  Work is highly independent.
raw_data.education_and_experience_substitution: An Associates Degree plus 2 additional years experience may be substituted for a Bachelors Degree.

labor_categories.years_experience: An Associates Degree plus 2 additional years experience may be substituted for a Bachelors Degree.
